usage: widget create <command> [<args> ...]

Create.

Flags:
  -v, --[no-]verbose  Enable verbose output.
  -c, --config="/etc/widget.yaml"  
                      Path to config file. ($WIDGET_CONFIG)
  -t, --tag=TAG ...   Tags to apply. Repeatable.

Commands:
  box          Box.
  rocket       Rocket.

